 thence, and cometh into the coasts of Judaea by the farther side of Jordan: and the people resort unto him again; and, as he was wont, he taught them again.","year":29},{"id":"recUrbD9XfPib00Oz","ref":"Mark.10.2","text":"And the Pharisees came to him, and asked him, Is it lawful for a man to put away his wife? tempting him.","year":29},{"id":"recuOPn66EazEvJsW","ref":"Mark.10.3","text":"And he answered and said unto them, What did Moses command you?","year":29},{"id":"recaTZGTUb3dlQPLH","ref":"Mark.10.4","text":"And they said, Moses suffered to write a bill of divorcement, and to put her away.","year":29},{"id":"rechaUF5UebDfbeSD","ref":"Mark.10.5","text":"And Jesus answered and said unto them, For the hardness of your heart he wrote you this precept.","year":29},{"id":"recodL1oRTIav9ywx","ref":"Mark.10.6","text":"But from the beginning of the creation God made them male and female.","year":29},{"id":"recewITvQbm5lqUAo","ref":"Mark.10.7","text":"For this cause shall a man leave his father and mother, and cleave to his wife;","year":29},{"id":"recjEzcJ6bOnHUn9Y","ref":"Mark.10.8","text":"And they twain shall be one flesh: so then they are no more twain, but one flesh.","year":29}]}
